article.headline: Bluefield College 65, Elon University 63
article.story: ELON, N.C. (AP) -- Jamaine Burcke scored 15 points and grabbed eight rebounds to lift Bluefield to a 65-63 win over Elon on Monday. Cedric Brown added 11 points and 11 rebounds for the Ramblin' Rams (8-7), who got 24 points off the bench. Four players scored double digits for Elon (2-10), led by Scottie Rice (18), Simon Harris (11), Chris Chalko (10), and Colin Wyatt, who scored 10 points off the bench. The Phoenix converted 23 Bluefield turnovers into 23 points and led 32-28 at the break. Bluefield shot 61.1 percent from the line.
